<view class="container">
  <view class="header">
    <text class="title">API配置</text>
  </view>

  <view class="config-area">
    <view class="info-text">请填入科大讯飞语音合成API的相关信息</view>
    
    <view class="config-item">
      <view class="config-label">App ID</view>
      <input class="config-input" value="{{appId}}" bindinput="onAppIdInput" placeholder="请输入APPID" />
    </view>
    
    <view class="config-item">
      <view class="config-label">API Key</view>
      <view class="input-wrapper">
        <input class="config-input" value="{{apiKey}}" bindinput="onApiKeyInput" 
              placeholder="请输入API Key" 
              password="{{!showApiKey}}" />
        <view class="toggle-btn" bindtap="toggleApiKeyVisibility">
          <text>{{showApiKey ? '隐藏' : '显示'}}</text>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
    
    <view class="config-item">
      <view class="config-label">API Secret</view>
      <view class="input-wrapper">
        <input class="config-input" value="{{apiSecret}}" bindinput="onApiSecretInput" 
              placeholder="请输入API Secret" 
              password="{{!showApiSecret}}" />
        <view class="toggle-btn" bindtap="toggleApiSecretVisibility">
          <text>{{showApiSecret ? '隐藏' : '显示'}}</text>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
  
  <view class="tips">
    <text class="tip-text">
      注意: 这些信息仅保存在您的设备上，不会上传到服务器。请妥善保管您的API密钥信息。
    </text>
  </view>

  <view class="button-area">
    <button class="btn save-btn" bindtap="saveConfig" disabled="{{isSaved}}">
      {{isSaved ? '已保存' : '保存配置'}}
    </button>
  </view>
</view> 